docs.abstract: George Floyd was killed by a police officer one year ago. His death galvanized a nation. How much do you think has changed since?
docs.snippet: George Floyd was killed by a police officer one year ago. His death galvanized a nation. How much do you think has changed since?
docs.lead_paragraph: On May 25, 2020, George Floyd was killed when a white police officer knelt on his neck for more than nine agonizing minutes. His death sparked an uprising for racial justice nearly unparalleled in American history, and many believed it might be a turning point in the way Americans confront issues of race and racism.

headline.main: How Much Have You and Your Community Changed Since George Floyd’s Death?

byline.original: By Nicole Daniels and Natalie Proulx

docs.abstract: The courts created qualified immunity for police. Reform means getting rid of it.
docs.snippet: The courts created qualified immunity for police. Reform means getting rid of it.
docs.lead_paragraph: When a Minneapolis jury last month convicted the former police officer Derek Chauvin of murdering George Floyd on May 25, 2020, many Americans celebrated. At last, a moment of accountability, if not quite justice, in the face of persistent police brutality.

headline.main: End the Court Doctrine That Enables Police Brutality
headline.print_headline: Holding  Cops  Liable, A Year  Later

docs.abstract: In addition to the disciplinary action they have faced, the boys’ mother said that at least one of her three sons has been bullied because of the shirts.
docs.snippet: In addition to the disciplinary action they have faced, the boys’ mother said that at least one of her three sons has been bullied because of the shirts.
docs.lead_paragraph: Two brothers, 8 and 5, were removed from their Oklahoma elementary school classrooms this past week and made to wait out the school day in a front office for wearing T-shirts that read “Black Lives Matter,” according to the boys’ mother.

headline.main: 2 Oklahoma Boys Pulled From Class for ‘Black Lives Matter’ T-Shirts
